data.description: Almost new home in desirable Highland Lakes which has an amazing open floor plan with 5 bedrooms and a bonus. Beautiful hardwoods throughout the main living area and upgraded hardwoods in main level bedroom. Granite counter tops and a trim package this is out of this world. Guest bedroom and study on the main level share a jack & jill bathroom. Great room with gorgeous fireplace that's open to the kitchen that is a chef's dream with a large beautiful island, 48 inch gas range, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry and range hood with a walk in pantry. 10ft ceilings/8ft doors throughout the first floor. Owner's suite on the 2nd floor with ensuite bath featuring garden tub, tiled extra large shower, dual vanities, water closet, and a spacious walk-in closet.
